Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,AI race is just
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.48,0:00:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,about Chatchy PT vs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.85,0:00:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Claude, you are missing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.05,0:00:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,half the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.33,0:00:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinese AI companies have
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.63,0:00:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,been cooking up something
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.67,0:00:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,serious,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.53,0:00:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and one name keeps
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.27,0:00:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,popping up in developer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.30,0:00:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,circles.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.19,0:00:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Moonshot AI's Kimi series.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.08,0:00:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, there is a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,new player on the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,block, Kimi K2 .5,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.05,0:00:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and it is making
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.67,0:00:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,some pretty bold claims.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.48,0:00:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But here's why you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,should care.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.98,0:00:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't just another
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,chatbot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a signal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.78,0:00:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of where AI is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,heading globally,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.10,0:00:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and the competition is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,about to get a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,lot more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.66,0:00:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to Moonshot AI founded
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.05,0:00:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,by former Google researcher
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.39,0:00:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yilu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.06,0:00:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This company has been
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.78,0:00:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,flying under the radar
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.74,0:00:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,while raking in serious
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.96,0:00:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,funding.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.65,0:00:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not just another
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.32,0:00:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,startup chasing the LLM
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.06,0:00:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,hype.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.46,0:00:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They've been systematically building
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,out their Kimi ecosystem
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,with versions ranging from
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,K0 to K2 and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.20,0:00:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,now K2 .5.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kimi series represents
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.10,0:00:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,their flagship offering,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.67,0:00:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and it is positioned
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.42,0:00:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,as a direct competitor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to the likes of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Biden's
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.43,0:00:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and Biden in the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.47,0:00:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinese AI landscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes them interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.93,0:00:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is their focus on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.88,0:00:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,making AI accessible
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,through an open platform
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.43,0:01:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,developers,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.39,0:01:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and businesses can actually
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.97,0:01:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,integrate Kimi into their
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.35,0:01:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,applications via API.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.26,0:01:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what exactly is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.21,0:01:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimi K2 .5 bringing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to the table?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kimi series has
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.01,0:01:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,been designed to handle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.01,0:01:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,various use cases,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,including conversation, analysis, and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.20,0:01:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,content generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.28,0:01:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Essentially covering the full
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,spectrum of LLM capabilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.01,0:01:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the platform at platform
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.21,0:01:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Moonshot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.09,0:01:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,AI gives developers direct
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.28,0:01:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,access to these models,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.51,0:01:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,meaning you can actually
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.65,0:01:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,build with Kimi right
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.28,0:01:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.18,0:01:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the progression from K0
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.40,0:01:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,through K1, K2,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.92,0:01:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and now K2 .5
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.01,0:01:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,suggests incremental improvements in
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.64,0:01:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,reasoning,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,context window, and multimodal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of K2 .5
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.98,0:01:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,as the most refined
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,iteration,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.92,0:01:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,yet faster responses, better
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.31,0:01:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,context understanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and more nuanced outputs
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.71,0:01:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,across different tasks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's where it gets
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How does Kimi K2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.56,0:01:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,.5 compare to what
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.76,0:01:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,we're seeing from Western
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.78,0:01:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,AI labs?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chinese AI market
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is fiercely competitive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,with Biden's and Baidu,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.81,0:01:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,both pushing their own
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.79,0:01:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,large language models.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.21,0:01:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Moonshot AI's edge seems
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.54,0:01:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to be their developer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:01:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-first approach
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and their rapid iteration
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.73,0:02:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.64,0:02:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,While we don't have
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.31,0:02:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,exact benchmark numbers for
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.73,0:02:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,K2 .5 publicly available
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the trajectory suggests they're
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.28,0:02:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,closing the gap with
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.25,0:02:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,GPT -4 and clawed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.78,0:02:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,in key areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.87,0:02:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The real advantage, integration
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,with Chinese language processing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.97,0:02:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and cultural context,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.58,0:02:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that Western models still
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.69,0:02:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,struggle with,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.59,0:02:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're building for
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,global or Chinese markets.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimi K2 .5 might
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.71,0:02:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,be worth a serious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.96,0:02:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,look.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.59,0:02:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the bottom line,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.78,0:02:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the AI world is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,getting bigger,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and Kimi K2 .5
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is proof that the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.81,0:02:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinese AI ecosystem
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't just catching up,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,they're innovating.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you are a
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.15,0:02:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,developer looking to integrate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,cutting edge AI,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.91,0:02:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,a tech enthusiast tracking
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.21,0:02:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the global AI race,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,or just someone who
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,wants to understand where
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,this technology is heading,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Moonshot AI deserves your
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The next year is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,going to be wild
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,as these models continue
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to evolve and compete,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,so keep your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,on Kimi because this
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is just the beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.24,0:02:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.47,0:02:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,what could be a
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,transformative shift in how
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,we think about AI
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.47,0:02:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit that subscribe button
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:02:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,if you want more
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:02:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,deep dives into the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:02:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,AI models.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.06,0:03:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaping our future, and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.31,0:03:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,drop a comment below.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,about the rise of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinese AI?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.06,0:03:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A.
